; Back side cavity pocket
; Tool: 2mm single flute spiral end mill
; Material: 3/16" brass on fixture plate
; X0 Y0 = plate center (BACK SIDE - brass flipped left-right)
; Z0 = top of brass

G21       ; metric
G90       ; absolute
G17       ; XY plane for arcs
M3 S10000 ; spindle on
G4 P2     ; spin-up dwell

; Cavity: circle r=35.052mm centred on plate centre
; Depth: 1.6mm (standard PCB thickness)
; Bit radius 1.0mm, stepover 1.0mm
; Center pin must be REMOVED before this op (the 3 tab pins still hold the part)

G0 Z5.0
G0 X0 Y0

